<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:10:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列警察法律顾问：警察不能在抗议活动中没收标语</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-legal-advisor-police-officers-cannot-confiscate-signs-at-protests/00000190-35e6-d8bc-abf7-b7f6848b0000</link><description>这些命令是在警察暴力没收抗议者标有反政府和战争口号的标语后向以色列高等法院提交请愿书后公布的。尽管如此，在没有法律授权的情况下，没收标志的行为仍在继续</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-legal-advisor-police-officers-cannot-confiscate-signs-at-protests/00000190-35e6-d8bc-abf7-b7f6848b0000</guid></item><item><title>面对与真主党迫在眉睫的战争，以色列有六个艰难的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/facing-a-looming-war-with-hezbollah-israel-has-six-tough-options/00000190-3434-d5f5-a5d6-fdfead7f0000</link><description>以色列正在应对与加沙哈马斯和胆大妄为的伊朗持续交战的前所未有的局势，同时决定如何应对与黎巴嫩真主党不断升级的跨境战斗。它的下一步行动必须以最经过计算和校准的方式完成——没有犯错的余地</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/facing-a-looming-war-with-hezbollah-israel-has-six-tough-options/00000190-3434-d5f5-a5d6-fdfead7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为何决定在 2025 年大阪世博会上低调亮相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-decided-to-lower-its-profile-at-expo-2025-in-osaka/00000190-2b43-d39e-a999-7fcf103b0000</link><description>世博会没有在显眼位置建造豪华展馆，而是在边缘选择了一个小得多的替代方案。 “在我看来，最好不要参与，”提交了原始提案之一的建筑师大卫·克纳福 (David Knafo) 说道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:55:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-decided-to-lower-its-profile-at-expo-2025-in-osaka/00000190-2b43-d39e-a999-7fcf103b0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列有两张脸”：他们逃离俄罗斯，却发现以色列有多相似</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-two-faces-they-escaped-russia-only-to-discover-how-similar-israel-is/00000190-2bf9-d39e-a999-7ffffa300000</link><description>乌克兰入侵后，艺术家维罗妮卡和丹尼尔·伯纳德从俄罗斯移居以色列。这里的生活是他们意想不到的一切：“我们正在努力保持理智和批判性思维”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-two-faces-they-escaped-russia-only-to-discover-how-similar-israel-is/00000190-2bf9-d39e-a999-7ffffa300000</guid></item><item><title>投资者是否正在撤离以色列？到目前为止，数字表明没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/are-investors-bailing-out-of-israel-so-far-the-numbers-say-no/00000190-3638-d39e-a999-76fe04a30000</link><description>对以色列持续投资的真正威胁不太可能是 BDS，而是政府的经济管理不善</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:28:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/are-investors-bailing-out-of-israel-so-far-the-numbers-say-no/00000190-3638-d39e-a999-76fe04a30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员警告电网尚未做好与真主党战争的准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-warns-power-grid-not-prepared-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-361c-d1b6-a19d-b7ffa7900000</link><description>“以色列断电 72 小时后，将无法居住，”负责电力系统监管的公司首席执行官表示。以色列电力公司迅速与“不负责任”的言论保持距离</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:11:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-warns-power-grid-not-prepared-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-361c-d1b6-a19d-b7ffa7900000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡助手对以色列第 13 频道新闻的愿景在泄露的谈话中透露</title><link>https: