me-on-the-street-but-i-have-gotten-death-threats-for-things-i-wrote/00000190-3564-d6fa-abb4-77ef9e4e0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名作家在以色列面临着作为一名创意人员的高潮和低谷，而一名男孩则在两个国家都有家</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/no-one-recognizes-me-on-the-street-but-i-have-gotten-death-threats-for-things-i-wrote/00000190-3564-d6fa-abb4-77ef9e4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将就国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的逮捕令请求支付 32,000 美元的律师费</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-32-000-in-legal-fees-for-iccs-arrest-warrant-requests-for-israeli-leaders/00000190-34f6-d690-a190-f4f723980000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官上个月因加沙战争向以色列总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长约阿夫·加兰特提出逮捕令后，以色列将向两名律师支付 12 万谢克尔的律师费</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 10:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-32-000-in-legal-fees-for-iccs-arrest-warrant-requests-for-israeli-leaders/00000190-34f6-d690-a190-f4f723980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长不会代表司法部长任命他选择的最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-will-not-represent-justice-minister-in-his-bid-to-appoint-a-supreme-court-president/00000190-349f-d690-a190-f49f3c050000</link><description>虽然以色列司法改革的设计者试图废除最高法院院长的资历制度，但以色列总检察长认为应该保留这一制度——它保证了法院的独立性，并将政治与任命过程分开</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-will-not-represent-justice-minister-in-his-bid-to-appoint-a-supreme-court-president/00000190-349f-d690-a190-f49f3c050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长禁止内塔尼亚胡任命下一任公务员专员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israels-attorney-general-bars-netanyahu-from-appointing-next-civil-service-commissioner/00000190-347b-d5f5-a5d6-fdfba4620000</link><descri